data.description: Wonderful Single Level Home on Large Corner Lot in Highly Sought After Santa Clara Location. Interior Features Spacious Living Room w/ Fireplace and Newer LVP Flooring, Primary Bedroom w/ Bathroom, and Custom Kitchen w/ Updated Cabinets, Flooring, and Appliances. Exterior Features Large Fenced Backyard, Patio, and Potential for Side RV parking. Also Don't Miss Super Low County Taxes! Wonderfully Cared for Inside and Out, a Must See.
